org.spongepowered.api.plugin

Annotation Type Dependency


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={})
public @interface Dependency
    Represents a dependency for a Plugin.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String id
      The plugin ID of the dependency.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean optional
      If this dependency is optional for the plugin to work.
      String version
      The required version range of the dependency.

    • Element Detail

      • id

        public abstract String id
        The plugin ID of the dependency.
        Returns:
        The dependency plugin ID
        See Also:
        Plugin.id()

      • version

        public abstract String version
        The required version range of the dependency.

        The version range will be specified in Maven version range syntax:

        RangeMeaning
        1.0Any dependency version, 1.0 is recommended
        [1.0]x == 1.0
        [1.0,)x >= 1.0
        (1.0,)x > 1.0
        (,1.0]x <= 1.0
        (,1.0)x < 1.0
        (1.0,2.0)1.0 < x < 2.0
        [1.0,2.0]1.0 <= x <= 2.0
        Returns:
        The required version range, or an empty string if unspecified
        See Also:
        Maven version range specification, Maven version design document
        Default:
        ""

      • optional

        public abstract boolean optional
        If this dependency is optional for the plugin to work. By default this is false.
        Returns:
        True if the dependency is optional for the plugin to work
        Default:
        false
